<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 06:10:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登怀疑斋月期间加沙停火，担心耶路撒冷暴力升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article-live/biden-doubts-gaza-cease-fire-by-ramadan-fears-escalating-violence-in-jerusalem/0000018e-2103-d7d3-abce-61ab371d0000</link><description>中央司令部否认周五美国空投杀害加沙平民 ■ 哈马斯呼吁巴勒斯坦人在斋月期间向圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺进军 ■ 布林肯与埃及外长交谈，讨论实现至少六周的停火 ■ 加拿大和西班牙表示将恢复向近东救济工程处提供资金 ■ 七名以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 02:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article-live/biden-doubts-gaza-cease-fire-by-ramadan-fears-escalating-violence-in-jerusalem/0000018e-2103-d7d3-abce-61ab371d0000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列士兵在约旦河西岸被爆炸装置炸伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-soldiers-wounded-by-explosive-devise-in-west-bank/0000018e-200f-df70-a1bf-67df5e910000</link><description>当士兵们追击巴勒斯坦人时，爆炸物被引爆，巴勒斯坦人向霍姆什前哨附近的以色列国防军哨所开枪。三人受中度伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 22:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-soldiers-wounded-by-explosive-devise-in-west-bank/0000018e-200f-df70-a1bf-67df5e910000</guid></item><item><title>非政府组织联盟表示，以色列拒绝续签约旦河西岸和加沙的援助人员签证，在关键时刻损害了援助工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/ngos-israel-pausing-aid-worker-visas-in-west-bank-gaza-harms-humanitarian-efforts/0000018e-1fb4-d7d3-abce-7fbdf55b0000</link><description>这个名为国际开发机构协会（AIDA）的联盟表示，其成员发挥了关键作用，并且在以色列与哈马斯加沙战争进行五个多月后迫切需要该联盟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 20:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/ngos-israel-pausing-aid-worker-visas-in-west-bank-gaza-harms-humanitarian-efforts/0000018e-1fb4-d7d3-abce-7fbdf55b0000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大表示将恢复向近东救济工程处提供资金，并援引该机构在加沙的“重要作用”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/canada-says-it-will-resume-unrwa-funding-cites-its-vital-role-in-gaza/0000018e-1fb7-df70-a1bf-7fff5e550000</link><description>在以色列指控近东救济工程处的 12 名工作人员参与了哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击后，包括美国和英国在内的 16 个捐助者暂停了对近东救济工程处的资助</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/canada-says-it-will-resume-unrwa-funding-cites-its-vital-role-in-gaza/0000018e-1fb7-df70-a1bf-7fff5e550000</guid></item><item><title>罗马道路连接加沙、希伯伦、耶路撒冷和提比里亚。今天他们还剩下什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/roman-roads-connected-gaza-hebron-jerusalem-and-tiberias-what-is-left-of-them-today/0000018e-18fe-d8fb-abff-5dfee1380000</link><description>以色列过去常常将其主要干道修建在古代伟大道路的上方或与之平行。新技术改变了这一点，但罗马路线仍然是一个未开发的旅游机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 19:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/roman-roads-connected-gaza-hebron-jerusalem-and-tiberias-what-is-left-of-them-today/0000018e-18fe-d8fb-abff-5dfee1380000</guid></item><item><title>“我不能只是坐在家里”：阿拉伯犹太人加沙援助车队运送食物和希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-couldnt-just-sit-at-home-the-arab-jewish-gaza-aid-convoy-carrying-food-and-hope/0000018e-1e72-df0d-adaf-9efee0d50000</link><description>在有关加沙地带越来越多的人死于饥饿的令人不安的报道中，一支由“站在一起”运动的阿拉伯犹太活动分子组成的车队出发前往凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，他们携带了两天的食物和一个罕见的信息跨国界的同理心</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 19:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-couldnt-just-sit-at-home-the-arab-jewish-gaza-aid-convoy-carrying-food-and-hope/0000018e-1e72-df0d-adaf-9efee0d50000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡陷入困境：战时内阁希望达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-in-a-corner-the-war-cabinet-wants-a-hostage-deal/0000018e-1f02-d7d3-abce-7faba2800000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 18:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-in-a-corner-the-war-cabinet-wants-a-hostage-deal/0000018e-1f02-d7d3-abce-7faba2800000</guid></item><item><title>“请原谅我在安息日结束时突然降临到你身上。我80岁的岳父现在在加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/excuse-me-for-descending-on-you-as-shabbat-ends-my-80-year-old-father-in-law-is-in-gaza/0000018e-1add-d7d3-abce-7afd32e60000</link><description>法庭判决中的合理性标准这样的抽象问题为何能够让数十万人走上街头，而参加加沙人质家属游行的人却少之又少？</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/excuse-me-for-descending-on-you-as-shabbat-ends-my-80-year-old-father-in-law-is-in-gaza/0000018e-1add-d7d3-abce-7afd32e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵开枪打死两兄弟，第三人受伤，第四人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-soldiers-shot-two-brothers-to-death-a-third-is-wounded-and-a-fourth-is-arrested/0000018e-1add-d8fb-abff-5fdf2eb80000</link><description>来自约旦河西岸的三兄弟和所有巴勒斯坦人一样，现在被禁止在以色列工作，他们翻过隔离墙采摘植物来养家糊口。在回来的路上，士兵向他们开枪</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-soldiers-shot-two-brothers-to-death-a-third-is-wounded-and-a-fourth-is-arrested/0000018e-1add-d8fb-abff-5fdf2eb80000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 154 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-1ee4-d1cc-abfe-dfed18030000</link><description>美国、英国、阿联酋和欧盟委员会组成的联盟宣布开放海上走廊，通过海上向加沙提供援助 ■ 中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯在访问埃及后抵达卡塔尔 ■ 在约旦河西岸非法前哨霍姆什爆炸，四名以色列人受伤■ 西班牙将恢复对近东救济工程处的资助 ■ 战争结束 154 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-1ee4-d1cc-abfe-dfed18030000</guid></item><item><title>“要么以色列成为一个真正的共和国，要么成为一个十字军国家——圣经和剑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/either-israel-becomes-a-true-republic-or-a-crusader-state-of-bible-and-sword/0000018e-1add-d8a6-a7de-3efd32a40000</link><description>科学史家阿夫纳·本扎肯认为，以色列所有问题的根源在于其选举制度。将其改为更直接、基于选区的系统可以改变我们的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:56:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/either-israel-becomes-a-true-republic-or-a-crusader-state-of-bible-and-sword/0000018e-1add-d8a6-a7de-3efd32a40000</guid></item><item><title>印度档案：以色列与印度极右翼的友好关系早在莫迪之前几十年就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-india-file-israels-warm-ties-with-the-indian-far-right-began-decades-before-modi/0000018e-19a9-d7d3-abce-79a999a10000</link><description>最近向公众公开的数千份以色列文件揭示了从 20 世纪 60 年代中期开始，以色列如何与印度的印度教民族主义政党建立关系 — — 尽管以色列外交官知道他们面对的是出于对穆斯林仇恨的极端分子</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-india-file-israels-warm-ties-with-the-indian-far-right-began-decades-before-modi/0000018e-19a9-d7d3-abce-79a999a10000</guid></item><item><title>拜登国情咨文：以色列在加沙浪费了美国的信贷额度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/bidens-state-of-the-union-israel-wasted-americas-credit-line-in-gaza/0000018e-1d98-d1cc-abfe-dfbd9e940000</link><description>美国开创了一个戏剧性的先例：以色列并不完全是加沙的发号施令者。如果以色列对抵抗外国势力在飞地的存在抱有幻想，那么临时港口的事实证明恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 13:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/bidens-state-of-the-union-israel-wasted-americas-credit-line-in-gaza/0000018e-1d98-d1cc-abfe-dfbd9e940000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院宣布部长解雇以色列邮政局主席的决定无效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/high-court-of-justice-nullifies-ministers-dismissal-of-israel-postal-services-chairman/0000018e-1d26-dd0d-a98f-9d2e3c380000</link><description>法官们裁定，内阁部长卡希和阿姆萨勒姆的决定无效，并且可能不利于以色列邮政正在进行的私有化进程。一位法官称解雇“极其不合理”</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/high-court-of-justice-nullifies-ministers-dismissal-of-israel-postal-services-chairman/0000018e-1d26-dd0d-a98f-9d2e3c380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学因学生反对而取消以巴冲突会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-cancels-conference-on-israel-palestine-conflict-after-students-object/0000018e-1d23-d1cc-abfe-dfaf9f410000</link><description>特拉维夫基布兹教育学院决定取消原计划举行的冲突历史教学会议，重点关注以色列和巴勒斯坦的叙述，此前一些学生和右翼活动人士认为该会议“敏感且具有攻击性”</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-cancels-conference-on-israel-palestine-conflict-after-students-object/0000018e-1d23-d1cc-abfe-dfaf9f410000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列准备应对国际社会对加沙的强烈反对，达成人质协议的可能性似乎很低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000</link><description>时任国防部长埃胡德·巴拉克 (Ehud Barak) 曾于 2011 年警告以色列可能遭遇“外交海啸”。当这种情况没有发生时，他的警告遭到了内塔尼亚胡的忠实支持者的嘲笑。但考虑到加沙旷日持久的战争，这就是以色列现在面临的问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是领导人，他应该受到责备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-head-he-is-to-blame/0000018e-1a76-d8fb-abff-5f7e5aae0000</link><description>15 年来，减去 18 个月的中断时间，以色列只有一位总理。近年来，他带领国家从灾难到灾难，从失败到失败，从崩溃到崩溃</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-head-he-is-to-blame/0000018e-1a76-d8fb-abff-5f7e5aae0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示“看起来很难”在斋月期间达成加沙停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-live/netanyahu-whoever-tells-us-not-to-act-in-rafah-is-telling-us-to-lose-the-war/0000018e-1c1d-d1cc-abfe-dfbd4b750000</link><description>布林肯与埃及外长交谈，讨论在加沙实现至少六周的停火 ■ 加拿大和西班牙表示将恢复向近东救济工程处提供资金 ■ 七名以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸爆炸中受伤 ■ 拜登宣布在加沙建立临时港口援助运送 ■ 美国在也门发动空袭，击落胡塞武装无人机</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-live/netanyahu-whoever-tells-us-not-to-act-in-rafah-is-telling-us-to-lose-the-war/0000018e-1c1d-d1cc-abfe-dfbd4b750000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在国情咨文中向以色列发出尖锐信息：不要将加沙援助作为讨价还价的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/biden-sends-sharp-message-to-israel-during-state-of-the-union-let-aid-into-gaza/0000018e-1bc3-d1cc-abfe-dfef36ee0000</link><description>“人道主义援助不能成为次要考虑因素或讨价还价的筹码。美国总统表示，保护和拯救无辜生命必须成为首要任务</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:27:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/biden-sends-sharp-message-to-israel-during-state-of-the-union-let-aid-into-gaza/0000018e-1bc3-d1cc-abfe-dfef36ee0000</guid></item><item><title>只有一个人知道内塔尼亚胡是否偿还了他的百万富翁朋友的贷款 - 但他并没有说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡获得了从斯宾塞·帕特里奇那里贷款的许可，后者此前曾给他买过雪茄和西装。这笔贷款是由总理亲自挑选的国家审计长批准的，该审计长应该通过内塔尼亚胡的资产和利息披露来监督还款，而公众无法获得这些信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</guid></item></channel></rss>